    <section class="hero">
        <h1>
            TatakTapulao
        </h1>
        <h2>COURIER SERVICES</h2>
        <h2>Helping connect Families over distance</h2>
        <div class="imageOfTheDayContainer">
            <img src="../images/hapkids.jpg" alt="imageOfTheDay" class="imageOfTheDay">
            <figcaption>
                An emotional moment from both sender and reciever of the Balikbayan Box.
                Truly, the boxes of love are a bonding instruments for families here and abroad.
                <br/>
                <br/>
                J. Ballesteros-Sender
            </figcaption>
